<li aria-level="1">00:47:50 What&#8217;s the Difference Between USB4 vs. Thunderbolt (3/4) Cables?
<ul>
<li aria-level="1">We are talking about cables with <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USB-C">USB-C ports</a>, not Lightning ports. So cables with USB-C ports mean USB and Thunderbolt cables.</li>
